[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Crash Site  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  The offending instruction is in `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcondition.[0m[1;92mc:100[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe call stack leading to the crash is:[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `src/shared/condition.c`  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `src/shared/condition.h`  [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mlink_config_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `src/udev/net/link-config.c`  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mlink_config_freep[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and then `[0m[1;35mlink_load_one[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the same file  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. `[0m[1;35mLLVMFuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `src/udev/net/fuzz-link-parser.c`  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Allocation and Free  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The memory region was allocated by `[0m[1;35mcondition_new[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcondition.[0m[1;92mc:73[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m during [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing of a “net condition” in `[0m[1;35mconfig_parse_net_condition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mnet-condition.[0m[1;92mc:213[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The same or overlapping structure is later freed by `[0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mcondition.[0m[1;92mc:96[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m as part of `[0m[1;35mconfig_parse_net_condition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and then freed again [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Observations  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The input is supplied by the fuzz harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`LLVMFuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls `[0m[1;35mlink_load_one[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` on the raw bytes.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The parsing routines involved include `conf-parser.c` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfunctions [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mnext_assignment[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mparse_line[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, and `[0m[1;35mconfig_parse[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and `net-condition.c`.  [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - The double-free or stale pointer access appears after the first free, when the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode iterates over a list of condition objects and tries to free them again.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Code Areas for Investigation  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  To understand the full scope of the bug, review:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • `src/shared/condition.c` and its list-freeing helpers  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • `src/shared/net-condition.c`, especially `[0m[1;35mconfig_parse_net_condition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • `src/shared/conf-parser.c`, where lines and assignments are parsed and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconditions are constructed  [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • `src/udev/net/link-config.c`, in particular `[0m[1;35mlink_load_one[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mlink_config_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    • The fuzz harness in `src/udev/net/fuzz-link-parser.c` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mas an entry point, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthough not the root cause[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname,i,n,head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m                           \[0m       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m165[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mLIST_LOOP_BUT_ONE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname,i,head,p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m                                \[0m       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:90[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m107[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m90[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m91[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m92:C[0m[39mondition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m93[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m94[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m95[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc->parameter[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m96[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mmfree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m97[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m98[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m99:C[0m[39mondition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:        return head;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/shared/condition.h:[0m[1;36m78[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m81[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m78:C[0m[39mondition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *first, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m79[0m[39m:static inline Condition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *first[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m80[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfirst, _CONDITION_TYPE_INVALID[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m81[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   The function `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `src/shared/condition.c` uses [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LIST_FOREACH` to iterate a linked list of `Condition` objects and calls [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in‐place. However, `LIST_FOREACH` only reads [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`c->conditions_next` each iteration by dereferencing the freed node, causing a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐use‐after‐free and double‐free when the list is later freed again in [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mlink_config_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Critical Logic to Preserve  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - On `type < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, free _all_ nodes and return a NULL head.  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - On `type >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, free only nodes whose `c->type` matches `type`, unlinking them[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mso the remaining list structure is intact.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Return the updated head of the list so that callers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mconfig_parse_net_condition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m correctly update their list pointer.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Do not alter any fuzz harness, test code, or external libraries.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Proposed Patch Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. Modify `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to use a _safe removal_ loop:  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Use `[0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to capture `n = [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mc->conditions_next` before freeing `c`.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - For each matching node, call `[0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to unlink [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit from the list, then `[0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - After the loop, `head` will either be NULL [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif `type < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` or all nodes [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatched[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or point to the sublist of unmatched nodes.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Return `head`, allowing callers to assign back into their pointers [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`*list [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m= [0m[33m...[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. Remove or retain the existing `[0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` as desired. With [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe safe unlinking, if `type < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`, `head` will end up NULL, satisfying the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39massertion.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c. No changes are required in headers, callers [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mconfig_parse_net_condition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, `[0m[1;35mlink_config_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, or harness code.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Outline  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   In `src/shared/condition.c` replace the existing definition:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Condition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return head;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   with:[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Condition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         Condition *c, *n;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Iterate safely, capturing next before possible free/unlink *[0m[35m/[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Unlink c from the list head, then free it *[0m[35m/[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[39m* If type<[0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, all nodes have been removed and head is NULL; else head[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            points to the sublist of unmatched nodes *[0m[35m/[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return head;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By capturing `n` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe next pointer[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m before any free, we avoid dereferencing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfreed memory on loop continuation.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Unlinking each freed node prevents dangling pointers in the list.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The returned `head` correctly represents the remaining list, ensuring that [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mupstream code [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `*list = [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*list, type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m maintains [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mproper ownership.  [0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No fuzz harness, tests, or external libraries are modified, preserving [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting coverage and validation.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The logic change only affects `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. Functionality for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnon‐`net` conditions [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., in other modules[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will also benefit from safe freeing, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith identical semantics.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing callers that ignore the return value of `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mwhich wraps `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m may carry a stale head pointer. However,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mall current callers either assign the return value back to their list variable [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35mconfig_parse_net_condition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` does[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m or immediately free the enclosing struct [0m[1;39m([0m[39min [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mlink_config_free[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so no live use of the old head remains.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The old `[0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` remains valid: when freeing all nodes [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`type < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the loop unlinks all elements, leaving `head == NULL`.  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Testing & Validation  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Re‐run the fuzz target [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`fuzz-link-parser`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m under AddressSanitizer; the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap‐use‐after‐free should no longer be triggered.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the existing test suite to verify no regressions in other [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Condition`‐related functionality.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mINFO:__main__:Running: docker run --privileged --shm-[0m[33msize[0m[39m=[0m[35m2g[0m[39m --platform linux/amd64[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m--rm -i -e [0m[33mHELPER[0m[39m=[0m[3;92mTrue[0m[39m -e [0m[33mARCHITECTURE[0m[39m=[0m[35mx86_64[0m[39m -v [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/qqor/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95msystemd[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mout[0m[39m -v [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/tmp/[0m[95mtmpfewhtnqc[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[95mtestcase[0m[39m -t ghcr.io/aixcc-finals/base-runner:v1.[0m[1;36m3.0[0m[39m reproduce [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzz-link-parser -[0m[33mruns[0m[39m=[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe fuzzer-triggered run of `fuzz-link-parser` uncovered an AddressSanitizer [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-use-after-free in the function `condition_free_list_type` [0m[1;39m([0m[39min [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`src/shared/condition.c`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. In response, a patch was proposed that replaces the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsafe `LIST_FOREACH` traversal with a `LIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT` loop and explicitly[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munlinks each node before freeing it. When this patch was applied and built, the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompiler rejected it with two `-Werror,-Wshadow` errors [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe loop macro re-declares[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration variables already declared locally[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and two `-Wunused-variable` warnings,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcausing the build to fail.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A fuzzing run of `fuzz-link-parser` produced a reproducible AddressSanitizer [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror:  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  “heap-use-after-free on address … in `condition_free_list_type`”  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace shows:  [0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Allocation of a `Condition` via `condition_new` in `condition.c`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Parsing of a net-condition in `net-condition.c` and building a linked list of [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Condition` nodes.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. A later call to `[0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhead, type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` iterates the list with [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and calls `[0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` whenever [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`c->type` matches or `type < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Because the list traversal macro does not account for removal during [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration, `condition_free` can free a node while the loop’s internal pointers [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill reference it, leading to a use-after-free when the next iteration accesses [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthat freed memory.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- File modified: `src/shared/condition.c`  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Original code around line [0m[1;36m97[0m[39m:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Condition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return head;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Proposed replacement:[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Declare two pointers up front: `Condition *c, *n;`[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Replace `LIST_FOREACH` with `[0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto capture `n = c->next` before freeing.[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Before `[0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, explicitly unlink `c` from `head` with [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. Keep the same return and assert.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The resulting patch snippet:[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Condition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      Condition *c, *n;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Iterate safely, capturing next before possible free/unlink *[0m[35m/[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Unlink c from the list head, then free it *[0m[35m/[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      return head;[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Result  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Build errors [0m[1;39m([0m[39mclang with `-Werror`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  src/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:103:47[0m[39m: error: declaration shadows a local variable [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m[[0m[39m-Werror,-Wshadow[0m[1;39m][0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                               ^[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  src/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:100:24[0m[39m: note: previous declaration is here[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      Condition *c, *n;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                         ^[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  src/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:103:44[0m[39m: error: declaration shadows a local variable [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m[[0m[39m-Werror,-Wshadow[0m[1;39m][0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                                            ^[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  src/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:100:20[0m[39m: note: previous declaration is here[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      Condition *c, *n;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    ^[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  warning: unused variable [0m[32m'c'[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m-Wunused-variable[0m[1;39m][0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  warning: unused variable [0m[32m'n'[0m[39m [0m[1;39m[[0m[39m-Wunused-variable[0m[1;39m][0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The macro `LIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT` itself declares iteration variables `c` and [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`n`, causing shadowing of the locally declared ones and triggering `-Werror` due to[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe project’s strict warning-as-error policy. The local declarations then become [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munused.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mCode Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Definitions of the list‐traversal macros in `src/basic/…` or wherever [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`LIST_FOREACH` and `LIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT` are defined. Understand how they [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclare or expect their iterator variables.  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The implementation of `condition_free` and `LIST_REMOVE` to confirm whether any [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madditional pointer updates are needed.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Callers of `condition_free_list_type`, particularly in `net-condition.c`, [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`conf-parser.c`, and `link-config.c`, to see how lists of `Condition` are built and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mused later.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname,i,n,head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m                           \[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m140[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtypeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39m*[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhead[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m *n, *i = [0m[1;39m([0m[39mhead[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; i && [0m[1;39m([0m[39mn = i->name##_next, true[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mi = n[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m141[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m142[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname,i,head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m                                       \[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m143[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, i, [0m[1;35mUNIQ_T[0m[1;39m([0m[39mn, UNIQ[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m144[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/basic/list.h:[0m[1;36m194[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m200[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mLIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head, free_func[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m       \[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35m_LIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head, free_func, [0m[1;35mUNIQ_T[0m[1;39m([0m[39melem, UNIQ[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35m_LIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head, free_func, elem[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m{[0m[39m                                              \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:99[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m107[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m99:C[0m[39mondition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:        return head;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/basic/list.h:[0m[1;36m190[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m209[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m190[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39m_p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m                                                 \[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m191[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, *_a, _p[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;                     \[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m192[0m[39m:                _p;                                                     \[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m193[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m194[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35mLIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head, free_func[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m       \[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35m_LIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head, free_func, [0m[1;35mUNIQ_T[0m[1;39m([0m[39melem, UNIQ[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m* Clear the list, destroying each element with free_func *[0m[35m/[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:#define [0m[1;35m_LIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head, free_func, elem[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m        \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m{[0m[39m                                              \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m201[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mtypeof[0m[1;39m([0m[39mhead[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m elem;                      \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:                while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39melem = [0m[1;35mLIST_POP[0m[1;39m([0m[39mname, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m   \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mfree_func[0m[1;39m([0m[39melem[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;                \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:                head;                                   \[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:[0m[35m/[0m[39m* Now include [0m[32m"macro.h"[0m[39m, because we want our definition of [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m which the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmacros above use. We include[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m: * it down here instead of up top, since macro.h pulls in log.h which in turn [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mneeds our own definitions. *[0m[35m/[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m209[0m[39m:#include [0m[32m"macro.h"[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:99[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m107[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m99:C[0m[39mondition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:        return head;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msrc/shared/condition.[0m[1;92mc:99[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m107[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;92m99:C[0m[39mondition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m100[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, head[0m[1;39m)[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || c->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:                        [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:        return head;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Remove the manual iterator declarations in `condition_free_list_type` and switch[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mto using the list‐library’s own safe‐iteration and clear macros without shadowing.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add a two-branch approach:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a. When `type < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfree all[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: call `[0m[1;35mLIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcondition_free[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. This macro unlinks and frees each node safely, returns a `NULL` [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mhead, satisfying the existing `[0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b. When `type >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m`: use `[0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdirectly [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno pre-declared `c, n`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and for each node whose `c->type == type`, [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvoke `[0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to unlink it, then `[0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`. [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis avoids UAF by capturing the `next` pointer before removal and freeing.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Retain the final `[0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and return the [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpossibly updated[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`head`.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. By relying on `LIST_CLEAR` and `LIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT`:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We avoid variable shadowing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno `-Wshadow` errors[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We avoid unused‐variable warnings.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We preserve the original API and harness behavior [0m[1;39m([0m[39mno harness or test [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchanges[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We keep all existing callers and behaviors intact, merely fixing the [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39muse-after-free bug.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Example updated implementation in `src/shared/condition.c`:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Condition* [0m[1;35mcondition_free_list_type[0m[1;39m([0m[39mCondition *head, ConditionType type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Free entire list safely and set head to NULL *[0m[35m/[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           head = [0m[1;35mLIST_CLEAR[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, condition_free[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Iterate safely, capturing next before removal/free *[0m[35m/[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;35mLIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, c, n, head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc->type == type[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[1;35mLIST_REMOVE[0m[1;39m([0m[39mconditions, head, c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                   [0m[1;35mcondition_free[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[39m* Ensure that if we requested a full clear, head is NULL *[0m[35m/[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35massert[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtype >= [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || !head[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       return head;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Justification:[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `LIST_CLEAR` internally performs a loop that pops each element from `head`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mupdates `head`, and calls the free function, guaranteeing no stale pointers or UAF.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - `LIST_FOREACH_WITH_NEXT` declares its own `c` and `n`, so no shadowed [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclarations remain.[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - We preserve the `assert` guarding the full‐list‐free invariant.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No external libraries, harness logic, or tests are modified.[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar idioms are used elsewhere in the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. `LIST_CLEAR` usage in [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mother cleanup functions[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, ensuring consistency and robustness.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This patch addresses both the UAF bug and the compiler warnings in a single, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mclean change. [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
